<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/steve-reed> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Steve Reed OBE was appointed Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government on 5 September 2025. He was previously Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Streatham and Croydon North in July 2024."@en .
